items.title: Awesome Codepoints
items.content_text:
### Standalone Code Points

*   [U+FF03](https://codepoints.net/U+FF03) FULLWIDTH NUMBER SIGN - it is the
    "Japanese Hashtag" `＃`. Sites like Twitter accept it as equivalent to the
    regular `#` ([U+0023](https://codepoints.net/U+0023)).

### Record Holders and Extremes / Breaking and Gluing other characters

*   U+1FBA8 BOX DRAWINGS LIGHT DIAGONAL UPPER CENTRE TO MIDDLE LEFT AND MIDDLE RIGHT TO LOWER CENTRE
    and
    U+1FBA9 BOX DRAWINGS LIGHT DIAGONAL UPPER CENTRE TO MIDDLE RIGHT AND MIDDLE LEFT TO LOWER CENTRE - longest name: 88
    characters each.
items.content_html:
Standalone Code Points

  • U+FF03 FULLWIDTH NUMBER SIGN - it is the "Japanese Hashtag" ＃. Sites like Twitter accept it as equivalent to the regular # (U+0023).

Record Holders and Extremes / Breaking and Gluing other characters

  • U+1FBA8 BOX DRAWINGS LIGHT DIAGONAL UPPER CENTRE TO MIDDLE LEFT AND MIDDLE RIGHT TO LOWER CENTRE and U+1FBA9 BOX DRAWINGS LIGHT DIAGONAL UPPER CENTRE TO MIDDLE RIGHT AND MIDDLE LEFT TO LOWER CENTRE - longest name: 88 characters each.

items.title: Awesome Cdk
items.content_text:
### Construct Libraries / Static Websites

*   [ness (⭐637)](https://github.com/nessjs/ness) - CDK powered CLI tool for deploying static sites to your AWS account.

### Construct Libraries / Workflows

*   [aws-pdf-textract-pipeline (⭐166)](https://github.com/aeksco/aws-pdf-textract-pipeline) - ETL pipeline for crawling PDFs from the Web using Puppeteer and transforming their contents into structured data using AWS Textract and storing the results in DynamoDB.
